// Package buzzgen contains Buzz trampolines for all host modules. Most files in
// this package are generated by magus-bindings-gen (-lang buzz); see the
// //go:generate directives in internal/std/*.go.
//
// Naming: host names stay snake_case in Buzz (read_file → read_file), matching
// the magusfile DSL. Multi-return Impls return a Buzz list [ret0, ret1, ...];
// host errors propagate as Buzz runtime errors.
package buzzgen
